# High-Frequency Trading Bot Cursor Rules

This is a high-frequency crypto trading bot that uses the CCXT MCP server for exchange integration.

## Key Features
- TypeScript/Node.js based
- Uses CCXT MCP server for exchange connectivity
- Implements multiple HFT strategies (scalping, arbitrage, market making, momentum)
- Real-time market data processing
- Position and risk management
- Paper trading and live trading modes

## Architecture
- src/strategies/ - Trading strategy implementations
- src/indicators/ - Technical indicators
- src/managers/ - Position, risk, and order managers
- src/utils/ - Utilities and configuration
- src/types/ - TypeScript type definitions

## MCP Integration
The bot uses the @doggybee/mcp-server-ccxt MCP server for exchange operations.

## Important
- Always validate inputs and handle errors
- Implement proper risk management
- Log all trading activities
- Test thoroughly in paper mode before live trading
